subtests.name: The timing allow check algorithm will pass when the Timing-Allow-Origin header value list contains a case-sensitive match.
The timing allow check algorithm will pass when the Timing-Allow-Origin header value list contains a wildcard.
The timing allow check algorithm will fail when the Timing-Allow-Origin header value list contains a null origin.
The timing allow check algorithm will pass when the Timing-Allow-Origin header value list contains the origin and a wildcard.
The timing allow check algorithm will pass when the Timing-Allow-Origin header value list contains multiple wildcards.
The timing allow check algorithm will pass when the Timing-Allow-Origin header value contains only the origin.
The timing allow check algorithm will fail when the Timing-Allow-Origin header value contains only the uppercased origin.
The timing allow check algorithm will fail when the Timing-Allow-Origin header value contains only a space.
The timing allow check algorithm will fail when the Timing-Allow-Origin header value contains only a wildcard.
The timing allow check algorithm will fail when the Timing-Allow-Origin header is not present.
